Document: VisualShaderNodeVec3Constant
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodevec3constant.rst
Summary: A constant Vector3 node used as an input in visual shaders.

A constant Vector3, which can be used as an input node. This node provides a fixed 3D vector value that can be connected to other nodes in a visual shader graph. The Vector3 value is specified through the node's properties and remains unchanged during shader execution.
